videos.headline: USF strikes first with Flowers' 63-yard TD run
videos.description: USF wastes no time in getting on the board needing only 1:11 of the clock before Quinton Flowers takes off 63 yards to the end zone putting the Bulls up 7-0 over Navy.

videos.headline: USF keeps rolling early with another TD run
videos.description: USF's offense can't be stopped so far when D'Ernest Johnson goes 23 yards up the middle to the end zone increasing the Bulls lead at 14-0.

videos.headline: USF keeps reeling off big plays
videos.description: USF strikes with another big play, this time Marlon Mack goes 85 yards to the house to give the Bulls a stunning 21-0 lead still in the first quarter.

videos.headline: USF makes it four TDs in the first quarter on a 41-yard TD pass
videos.description: After rushing for three touchdowns, USF goes through the air when Quinton Flowers finds a streaking Elkanah Dillon for a 41-yard touchdown to continue the Bull's stunning start that's now at 28-0 over Navy.

videos.headline: USF makes it five TDs on its opening five drives
videos.description: Navy can't stop USF's high powered offense, especially when Quinton Flowers uses a nasty juke move to get around a defender and score from a yard out to make it 35-7 for the Bulls.

videos.headline: W. Worth run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.headline: USF scores sixth TD on sixth drive of the game
videos.description: For the sixth time USF got the ball and like all five time before, the Bulls finish this drive off with a touchdown, this one a 17-yard pass to Marquez Valdes-Scantling to extend USF's lead at 42-14.

videos.headline: Navy clawing back with TD capping a 99-yard drive
videos.description: USF was cruising early but Navy has been working its way back into the game, cutting the lead to 45-27 with a touchdown on fourth down.

videos.headline: Navy fumbles on the goal line, fail on two-point conversion
videos.description: Navy fumbles on the goal line, fail on two-point conversion

videos.headline: USF finds the end zone again, puts end to Navy comeback
videos.description: Navy had started clawing its way back into the game until USF struck again when D'Ernest Johnson gets through the line and hits pay dirt from 16 yards out to increase the lead to 52-27.
